snippet.title: Harpooned 2009 update
snippet.description:
Download Harpooned for free at: http://harpooned.org -  Harpooned 2009 update - new features include:
New 'capture protesters' ability.
Mac version now available.
Online leaderboards allow you to compete with other scientists worldwide.
